title: Crunchy Onion Chicken & Noodle Dinner
directions: Stir soup, milk, 1 cup French Fried Onions, vegetables, chicken, noodles and 1/2 cup cheese in a 2-qt. baking dish.
Bake at 350°F for 30 min. or until hot. Stir.
Top with remaining cheese and French Fried Onions. Bake 5 min. until onions are golden.
ingredients: 1 (10 3/4 ounce) can Campbell's® Condensed Cream of Chicken Soup
2 cups (4 oz.) FRENCH'S® Original French Fried Onions
1 cup frozen vegetables of your choice
2 cups cubed cooked chicken or turkey
2 cups curly egg noodles, cooked and drained
